## âœ¨ Features

- ðŸ” Search Unicode characters by name (strict or fuzzy match)
- âš¡ Multiple fuzzy matching algorithms:
  - `difflib.SequenceMatcher` (standard lib)
  - [`rapidfuzz`](https://github.com/maxbachmann/RapidFuzz)
  - [`python-Levenshtein`](https://github.com/ztane/python-Levenshtein)
- ðŸ“š Unicode NFKD normalization for accurate comparison
- ðŸ’¾ Local cache to speed up repeated lookups
- ðŸŽ¨ CLI color support via `colorama`
- ðŸ§ª Full test suite: unit tests + CLI tests via `pytest`
- ðŸ Usable both as CLI and as Python library
- ðŸ“¦ Modern `pyproject.toml`-based packaging (PEP 621)
- ðŸ”„ GitHub Actions CI with multi-version Python matrix and Coveralls integration
- ðŸ”§ Pre-commit hooks for formatting, type checking, and linting

